      <title>英国工党将保持“财政审慎”预算：PGIM</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/labour-to-remain-fiscally-prudent-in-uk-budget-pgim-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PGIM 首席欧洲经济学家 Katharine Neiss 讨论了即将到来的英国秋季预算，并表示她预计工党政府将在 Rachel Reeves 的声明中保持“财政审慎”。她还讨论了预算声明对债券市场可能意味着什么。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/labour-to-remain-fiscally-prudent-in-uk-budget-pgim-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
