      <title>大众汽车盈利能力降至疫情以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/vw-profitability-shrinks-to-lowest-since-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团的营业利润率降至新冠疫情爆发以来的最低水平，该疫情迫使该汽车制造商停产并关闭展厅。彭博社的 Oliver Crook 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/vw-profitability-shrinks-to-lowest-since-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
