      <title>阿斯顿·马丁希望通过降低成本帮助汽车制造商结束亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/aston-martin-counts-on-cost-drive-to-help-carmaker-end-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该豪华汽车制造商报告另一季度亏损后，阿斯顿·马丁Lagonda Global Holdings Plc 首席执行官 Adrian Hallmark 承诺加大成本削减力度。]]></description>
